title: Every Tory cabinet minister is a eurosceptic, Michael Fallon says
text: Every minister in David Cameron’s cabinet is a eurosceptic, the defence secretary has said. Michael Fallon said there was nobody around the cabinet table who was particularly enthusiastic about the European Union. “I think we’re all eurosceptics now. I don’t see any eurofanatics around the cabinet table,” he told BBC One’s Andrew Marr Show.
